room_title: Escape room "NXT-GEN" by Alternate Reality Escape Rooms in Houston
room_description: In 1941, The Government put together a contingency plan in preparation of a catastrophic event. Fast forward 80 years and the human race is going extinct.  Project Nxt-Gen has run into a few malfunctions and we need you to fix them! We are counting on you to save us! Will you be successful or will man kind end with this last mission?
